00:22:02.342 --> 00:22:05.636
"Please guide me to continue to appreciate these gifts"

00:22:05.678 --> 00:22:10.558
"and share my good fortune and plenty with others in this world."

00:22:10.808 --> 00:22:14.687
"The world is full of infinite possibilities!"

00:22:16.773 --> 00:22:21.736
Nice words and they very naturally express their gratitude to many things,

00:22:22.111 --> 00:22:25.281
and extend their warm hearts to others.

00:22:27.200 --> 00:22:30.703
